    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Order of the Lycan</em></p><p>As a bonus action, you mark a creature that you can see within 30 feet of you. Until the end of your next turn, while you are in your hybrid form, you gain temporary hit points eqaul to any crimson rite damage you deal to the creature.</p><p>Temporary hit points gained from multiple attacks are considered from the same source and add together.<br /><br /><strong>Amplify</strong>. This curse lasts up to 1 minute. Starting after the end of your next turn, the cursed creature can make a Charisma saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the curse on itself on a success</p>",
